Package org.matsim.contrib.minibus.replanning

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PStrategy  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CreateNew24hPlan
    Creates a completely new 24h plan.
    CreateNewPlan
    Creates a new plan from scratch.
    EndRouteExtension
    Takes the route transformed into a lineString to calculate a buffer around it.
    MaxRandomEndTimeAllocator
    Sets a new endTime between the old endTime and midnight.
    MaxRandomStartTimeAllocator
    Changes the start time of operation randomly from midnight to startTime.
    PStrategyManager
    Loads strategies from config and chooses strategies according to their weights.
    ReduceStopsToBeServedRFare
    Removes all stops belonging to a demand relation with trips below a certain threshold.
    ReduceTimeServedRFare
    Restricts the time of operation to temporal relations higher than a certain threshold.
    SidewaysRouteExtension
    Takes the route transformed into a lineString to calculate a buffer around it.
    WeightedEndTimeExtension
    Changes the end time of operation by drawing randomly a new time slot from endTime to midnight.
    WeightedStartTimeExtension
    Changes the start time of operation by drawing randomly a new time slot from midnight to startTime.
